race.description: Amj Engineering & Fabrication Capalaba Futurity H
race.comment: IDEA'S GIRL (5) recorded a 1.5 lengths win (19.83) in a Grade 3/4 last time at this track. Has already won four times from this draw. Expected to be in the finish. GYPSY GIRL PEARL (4) failed to come into contention last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won by half a length at Q Parklands (34.66) beating Whiskey Service in a Grade 4/5 on November 8. Worth another chance. ZIPPING CHOI (2) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 6 lengths (19.61) at this track. Harder here but expected to measure up. HARA'S PUMPKIN (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.
